comments: All the words ended with "ckuh", apart from the blue and yellow pentagons which were sometimes "ckuh" and sometimes "ckoh". Apart from the blue and yellow pentagons (sometimes), there was no way to distinguish between different colours of the same shape, and this made the final test unfair, as the word did not fully describe the shape and there were always at least two, and usually four, equally valid answers - only one of which was correct.
